paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

spdf_sza = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///sun/kasi_sun_angle.parquet')
spdf_sza.sort('date', 'time').show()

paragraphs.title: use cas_simple dataset
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from datetime import datetime

udf_objdt2strdt = udf(lambda objdt: objdt.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'), StringType())

cas = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/simple.parquet')
cas.show(1)
spdf_cas = cas.withColumn('datetime', udf_objdt2strdt('datetime'))\
              .withColumn('date', udf_dt2d('datetime'))\
              .withColumn('time', udf_dt2t('datetime'))\
              .select('date', 'time', 'illum', 'cct', 'swr', 'uvi', 'tri_x', 'tri_z')

spdf_cas.printSchema()

%pyspark
import pandas as pd
gw_cct_anomaly = spark.createDataFrame(pd.read_csv('/home/witlab/gw_cct_anomaly.csv'))
gw_cct_anomaly.show()
spdf_cctanon = gw_cct_anomaly.select('date', 'time', 'isErr').cache()
spdf_cctanon.printSchema()

%pyspark

udf_time = udf(lambda s: s[:-3], StringType())

spdf_cctanon = gw_cct_anomaly.withColumn('time', udf_time('time'))\
                             .select('date', 'time', 'isErr').cache()
spdf_cctanon.printSchema()

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dnt2dt

main_spdf = spdf_cas.join(spdf_sza, ['date', 'time'])

main_spdf.sort('date', 'time').show()

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType

udf_scaler = udf(lambda s: s / 10000, DoubleType())
ds = main_spdf.select('date', 'time', 'illum', 'swr', 'uvi', 'solar_zenith', 'tri_x', 'tri_z')\
              .withColumn('illum_scaled', udf_scaler('illum'))
ds.show()

%pyspark
import numpy as np
spdf_train_b, spdf_test = ds.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)
spdf_train, spdf_val = spdf_train_b.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)

pdf_train = spdf_train.toPandas()
pdf_val = spdf_val.toPandas()
pdf_test = spdf_test.toPandas()

x_train = np.array(pdf_train[['illum_scaled', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'tri_x', 'tri_z']])
y_train = np.array(pdf_train['uvi'])

x_val = np.array(pdf_val[['illum_scaled', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'tri_x', 'tri_z']])
y_val = np.array(pdf_val['uvi'])

x_test = np.array(pdf_test[['illum_scaled', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'tri_x', 'tri_z']])
y_test = np.array(pdf_test['uvi'])

print('x_train:', len(x_train), 'x_val:', len(x_val), 'x_test:', len(x_test))
print('y_train:', len(y_train), 'y_val:', len(y_val), 'y_test:', len(y_test))

%pyspark
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense, Activation
from keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping

nodes = 32
epochs = 500
batch_size = 128

model = Sequential()
model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform', input_dim=5))
model.add(Activation('relu'))
model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform'))
model.add(Activation('relu'))
model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform'))
model.add(Activation('relu'))
model.add(Dense(1))

model.compile(optimizer='adam', loss='mae', metrics=['mse'])

early_stopping = EarlyStopping(patience=20)

model.fit(x_train, y_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size,
          validation_data=(x_val, y_val),
          callbacks=[early_stopping])
